tspan.tspan: Choose up to five falling creatures within
range. A falling creature's rate of descent slow
s to 60 feet per round until the spell ends. If
the creature lands before the spell ends, it
takes no falling damage and can land on its
feet, and the spell ends for that creature.

text.tspan: A small feather or piece of down.
When you or a creature within 60 feet falls.
